":544,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.copyParentsTo","doc":"Copy `parents` to the parents of `root`.\n`root` must be the root of its equivalence class.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.copyParentsTo\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">copyParentsTo</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(parents : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.ParentSet\">Lean.Meta.Grind.ParentSet</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(root : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM\">Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.lean#L536-L542","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.getParentsAndReset","line":536,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.getParentsAndReset","doc":"Similar to `getParents`, but also removes the entry `e ↦ parents` from the parent map.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.getParentsAndReset\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">getParentsAndReset</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(e : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"