zed `True` expression.  "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.isTrueExpr\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">isTrueExpr</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(e : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GrindM\">Lean.Meta.Grind.GrindM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.lean#L133-L140","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.canon","line":133,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.canon","doc":"Canonicalizes nested types, type formers, and instances in `e`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.canon\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">canon</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(e : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GrindM\">Lean.Meta.Grind.GrindM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.lean#L124-L131","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.shareCommon","line":124,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.shareCommon","doc":"Applies hash-consing to `e`. Recall that all expressions in a `grind` goal have\nbeen hash-consing. We perform this step before we internalize expressions.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.shareCommon\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">shareCommon</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(e : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GrindM\">Lean.Meta.Grind.GrindM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.lean#L115-L122","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.abstractNestedProofs","line":115,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.abstractNestedProofs","doc":"Abtracts nested proofs in `e`. This is a preprocessing step performed before internalization.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.abstractNestedProofs\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">abstractNestedProofs</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(e : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind